        "created_at": "2024-12-22T23:47:56.793Z",
        "cooked": "<p>When you have a vertical gradient as your color in chats, the color of chats seems to be based on the fixed position of the gradient a certain part of your screen. This means that when you open your keyboard, the messages lowest on the screen might drastically change color, which is a bit jarring. I feel that it might be a little more visually pleasing to also have the gradient shift up <em>with</em> the keyboard, so that there’s no color change at the lowest level (this is similar to what iMessage does). Here’s an example of what this looks like in Signal:<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/e/d/ed7f16665e65b6d44a1a935cd5ae43b2f3efa1e4.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/ed7f16665e65b6d44a1a935cd5ae43b2f3efa1e4\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/e/d/ed7f16665e65b6d44a1a935cd5ae43b2f3efa1e4_2_172x375.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"xSZrxxiuvli1nidHs7k2paN2Khe\" width=\"172\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/e/d/ed7f16665e65b6d44a1a935cd5ae43b2f3efa1e4_2_172x375.jpeg, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/e/d/ed7f16665e65b6d44a1a935cd5ae43b2f3efa1e4_2_258x562.jpeg 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/e/d/ed7f16665e65b6d44a1a935cd5ae43b2f3efa1e4_2_344x750.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"156CA3\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">945×2048 172 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div> <div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/7/8/786f84b1c745e597a81b839829246f1269d41ab9.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/786f84b1c745e597a81b839829246f1269d41ab9\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/7/8/786f84b1c745e597a81b839829246f1269d41ab9_2_172x375.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"hbqdQIcoPySdmpX7AQyIxrTyNUB\" width=\"172\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/7/8/786f84b1c745e597a81b839829246f1269d41ab9_2_172x375.jpeg, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/7/8/786f84b1c745e597a81b839829246f1269d41ab9_2_258x562.jpeg 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/7/8/786f84b1c745e597a81b839829246f1269d41ab9_2_344x750.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"295F77\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">945×2048 130 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>And here’s what it looks like in iMessage:</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/d/d/dd814745d444a87051c4df3b71dff4349bad9594.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/dd814745d444a87051c4df3b71dff4349bad9594\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/d/d/dd814745d444a87051c4df3b71dff4349bad9594_2_172x375.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"vBwuUWhsE2pGxxSHcplMg9d2R4E\" width=\"172\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/d/d/dd814745d444a87051c4df3b71dff4349bad9594_2_172x375.jpeg, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/d/d/dd814745d444a87051c4df3b71dff4349bad9594_2_258x562.jpeg 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/d/d/dd814745d444a87051c4df3b71dff4349bad9594_2_344x750.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"296495\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">945×2048 141 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div> <div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/a/c/acabb81e1c8bec65d1876a536176a4b3ff2169b9.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/acabb81e1c8bec65d1876a536176a4b3ff2169b9\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/a/c/acabb81e1c8bec65d1876a536176a4b3ff2169b9_2_172x375.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"oDw1XzxsRfQmPCMFhNvfCC9UB4t\" width=\"172\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/a/c/acabb81e1c8bec65d1876a536176a4b3ff2169b9_2_172x375.jpeg, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/a/c/acabb81e1c8bec65d1876a536176a4b3ff2169b9_2_258x562.jpeg 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/a/c/acabb81e1c8bec65d1876a536176a4b3ff2169b9_2_344x750.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"2D4D6C\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">945×2048 109 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>",
